WEBVTT

00:00:00.585 --> 00:00:05.101
-YOM HASHMONA ESRE LENOVEMBER, ELEF TISHA MEOT VESHESH.

00:00:04.348 --> 00:00:05.152
JA.

00:00:05.479 --> 00:00:06.873
yetst meg ikh vayter dos?

00:00:06.441 --> 00:00:07.346
yo.

00:00:07.183 --> 00:00:08.544
der mayor

00:00:09.006 --> 00:00:13.076
hot tsu maynem glik, tsu undzern glik, nisht gut gelebt mitn prefekt

00:00:13.076 --> 00:00:16.506
azoy az se kumt shoyn for. zey hobn nisht gehat beyde ⟨eyn diz⟩

00:00:16.521 --> 00:00:18.444
vi ikh hob im gevizn dem tsetl

00:00:18.444 --> 00:00:22.444
vos der prefekt hot geshribn, az UNK fine- fir un tsvantsik sho

00:00:22.444 --> 00:00:24.609
zol men undz shikn tsu ibern Bug

00:00:24.767 --> 00:00:26.350
hot er nor gezogt

00:00:26.350 --> 00:00:27.616
oyf rumenish

00:00:27.616 --> 00:00:29.740
"der hunt shikt aykh in toyt arayn."

00:00:29.740 --> 00:00:32.250
dos hot "nor ikh vel aykh makhn a, a figur."

00:00:32.985 --> 00:00:40.466
er hot in Shargorod, dos iz geven draysik kilometer vayter, iz geven oykh a lager, azoy vi Mo- Tshe- Mogilev iz geven Shargorod

00:00:40.466 --> 00:00:42.631
un in Shargorod iz geven

00:00:42.790 --> 00:00:44.558
der, a yid

00:00:44.558 --> 00:00:51.998
a gevezener tsienist TEICH, dokter TEICH, a barimter tsienist demlst, geven zayner a khaver fun SUCEAVA fun Rumenye

00:00:52.307 --> 00:00:57.076
hot m- hot er undz bay nakht avekgeshikt ahin, di eltern un mikh, ⟨mit⟩ zi

00:00:57.572 --> 00:01:00.755
un dort hot undz der dokter TEICH oyfgenumen

00:01:01.352 --> 00:01:06.189
un hot mikh gegebn SOFORT arbet als saniter az ikh zol nisht darfn geyn tsu der arbet

00:01:06.347 --> 00:01:08.416
un dos iz geven a groys glik

00:01:08.440 --> 00:01:10.183
vayl shpeter a yor

00:01:10.183 --> 00:01:12.033
az der krig hot ongehoybn

00:01:12.033 --> 00:01:16.283
un di rusn zenen arayn NACH Mogilev, zey hobn bafrayt Mogilev fun di rumener

00:01:16.283 --> 00:01:19.464
iz der komandant geven a Mogilever

00:01:19.464 --> 00:01:21.900
un hot gefregt "vu iz mayn mishpokhe?"

00:01:22.142 --> 00:01:24.620
hot men gezogt "di, di rumenishe yidn

00:01:24.620 --> 00:01:30.644
az m'hot gedarft shikn ergets oyf arbet, hobn zey geshikt zey undzere mentshn, un zey r- hot, hot men nisht azoy genumen

00:01:30.644 --> 00:01:32.666
un zenen ale dort umgekumen.

00:01:32.723 --> 00:01:34.961
hot er gemakht mobilizatsye

00:01:35.085 --> 00:01:39.553
un ale ⟨yingere⟩ mentshn, azoy vi ikh bin geven un nokh, nokh hunderter

00:01:39.553 --> 00:01:41.401
hot men geleygt in vagon

00:01:41.401 --> 00:01:46.638
un me hot zey gefirt NACH Rusland, me zol zey lernen, ⟨zey zoln⟩ darfn geyn in der milkhome. dos iz geven fir un fertsik nokh.

00:01:47.505 --> 00:01:49.476
un dos iz geven mayn glik vos ikh

00:01:49.476 --> 00:01:53.321
bin geven in Shargorod. dortn hot men nisht gemakht keyn mobilizatsye

00:01:53.361 --> 00:01:54.294
un dort

00:01:54.294 --> 00:01:57.129
vi di CHAYALIM zenen gekumen in Bryansk

00:01:57.129 --> 00:01:58.749
iz der komandant funem

00:01:58.749 --> 00:02:01.454
funem BAHNHOF geven a, a shpyon

00:02:01.512 --> 00:02:07.345
un hot gegebn di daytshe tsu visn az s'iz do vagonen mit y- mit yidn, mit rusn

00:02:07.872 --> 00:02:09.705
mit,

00:02:09.797 --> 00:02:11.895
UNK geyn oyf der front

00:02:11.895 --> 00:02:14.241
iz gekumen AVERONIM. m'hot bombardirt

00:02:14.241 --> 00:02:15.711
hundert tsvontsik

00:02:15.711 --> 00:02:22.591
hundert tsvontsik yid- yidn UNK vos hobn ibergelebt TRANSNISTRIA vos zenen dort geharget gevorn, unter dem mayne khaveyrim oykh

00:02:20.192 --> 00:02:21.148
yetst

00:02:22.622 --> 00:02:23.645
a sakh.

00:02:22.723 --> 00:02:26.335
yetst di, di dray yor in di lager

00:02:25.052 --> 00:02:25.749
yo

00:02:25.749 --> 00:02:26.531
JA

00:02:26.335 --> 00:02:29.105
du bist geven mit di froy ⟨tsunezamen⟩?

00:02:27.398 --> 00:02:29.957
mit di froy mit di eltern tsuzamen

00:02:29.755 --> 00:02:33.035
du kenst yetst tseyln oyf di dray yor?

00:02:31.583 --> 00:02:32.539
yo.

00:02:32.747 --> 00:02:36.217
JA, s'iz, undz ho'mir gevoynt ⟨AUSSER⟩ fun dem geto

00:02:36.217 --> 00:02:38.937
un mayn MUTTER iz JUNG un in gortn hot genumen

00:02:38.937 --> 00:02:42.857
IRAKOT un m'hot getrogn in geto gegebn bakente dort, zol zey nokh

00:02:42.857 --> 00:02:44.747
a bisl veynikstns helfn

00:02:44.762 --> 00:02:47.118
un ikh hob eyn mol, m'hot gezogt

00:02:47.175 --> 00:02:48.454
az in Mogilev

00:02:48.454 --> 00:02:49.273
nemt men

00:02:49.273 --> 00:02:51.044
UNK lager

00:02:51.044 --> 00:02:52.268
firt men mentshn.

00:02:52.268 --> 00:02:54.521
me zol f- gikher ⟨gehargenen⟩ kenen

00:02:54.521 --> 00:02:58.892
hob ikh in dem gortn iz geven a kamer dort, hob ikh bahaltn akht mentshn

00:02:58.892 --> 00:03:02.289
bakente vos zenen nokh haynt in ISRAEL do a teyl fun zey.

00:03:02.397 --> 00:03:07.827
un hobn zey dort bahaltn. hobn zey yedn trog getrogn a flash vaser un a shtikele broyt, zoln nisht shtarbn far hunger

00:03:07.827 --> 00:03:09.997
biz s'iz ibergegangen di aktsye.

00:03:10.041 --> 00:03:12.856
vayl di vos me hot avekgeshikt dortn oyf SCAZINETI

00:03:12.856 --> 00:03:16.296
zenen shoyn nisht mer tsurikgekumen. ikh hob di akht geratevet.

00:03:16.909 --> 00:03:18.028
un i-

00:03:18.028 --> 00:03:20.261
bin gegangen eyn mol fun der arbet

00:03:20.352 --> 00:03:22.250
un hob getrogn dos shtikl broyt

00:03:22.250 --> 00:03:27.640
un in geto in di gas zenen geshtanen yidn, hobn gemakht politik un m'hot geredt ven vet shoyn zayn di yeshie

00:03:27.640 --> 00:03:31.528
hob ikh getrofn dort a bakantn fun Tshernovits, a groysn soykher

00:03:31.528 --> 00:03:32.766
iz geshtanen

00:03:33.126 --> 00:03:35.364
un hot gekukt oyf dem shtikl broyt

00:03:35.657 --> 00:03:37.198
ikh hob es im gegebn.

00:03:37.198 --> 00:03:40.966
dray tog shpeter ⟨oder⟩ fir tog shpeter iz er shoyn oyf say vi say geven geshtorbn.

00:03:42.475 --> 00:03:45.478
vifl m'hot mitgemakht, m'hot, m'hot gegloybt

00:03:45.478 --> 00:03:47.548
m'hot gem- nisht gegleybt ven es vet zikh

00:03:47.548 --> 00:03:50.078
endikn der krig. m'hot nisht gornisht gevust.

00:03:50.078 --> 00:03:51.803
bay nakht iz men gezesn

00:03:51.803 --> 00:03:54.968
bay a kleyn ka- a fleshele mit neft

00:03:54.968 --> 00:03:58.258
mit a kleynem ⟨diz⟩ un azoy iz men gezesn bay nakht.

00:03:58.258 --> 00:04:00.913
un az s'hot zikh shoyn gedarft endikn der krig

00:04:01.476 --> 00:04:04.440
zenen di, di rusishe trupn

00:04:04.581 --> 00:04:05.520
di

00:04:05.526 --> 00:04:06.903
di n-

00:04:07.348 --> 00:04:09.890
di, nisht di, di rusishe

00:04:10.791 --> 00:04:16.168
biz van- ver hot ZURUCKGEZOGEN SIE, DIE DEUTSCH- JA, di rusishe trupn hobn zikh tsurikgetsoygn

00:04:18.012 --> 00:04:21.550
di daytshe, di daytshe trupn, PARDON, fun Stalingrad

00:04:22.958 --> 00:04:24.271
iz gevorn nakht

00:04:24.271 --> 00:04:27.694
zenen zey geven in dem dorf vu undz ho'mir gevoynt, in a dorf

00:04:27.902 --> 00:04:31.456
zenen zey gan- -volt shlofn, zenen zey gekumen bay di tir un hobn geklopt.

00:04:31.632 --> 00:04:32.734
makh ikh oyf.

00:04:32.734 --> 00:04:39.320
shteyt eyner un heybt un oyf- tsu redn rusish, vos zey zenen geven oyf der front in Stalingrad hobn zey gekent a por verter rusish.

00:04:39.377 --> 00:04:43.438
UNK az ikh zol zikh mutshen a bisl un zol redn yidish UNK gezogt

00:04:43.512 --> 00:04:45.784
"SIE KONNEN MIR DAS SAGEN AUF DEUTSCH."

00:04:46.347 --> 00:04:52.028
er hot gevert, iz er arayngekumen, "KAMERADEN, HIER SPRICHT MAN DEUTSCH, ⟨IHR SINT UNSERIGE⟩." gemeynt ikh bin a

00:04:52.388 --> 00:04:57.818
arayngekumen, arayngebrakht, zey hobn gehat esn, zakhn vos undz ho'mir dray yorn nisht gezen un m'hot zey

00:04:57.818 --> 00:04:59.621
nokh dem kukt er mikh on, zogt er

00:05:00.049 --> 00:05:01.510
"DU BIST EIN DEUTSCHE. DU B- DU

00:05:01.510 --> 00:05:05.480
DU WILLST NICHT KAMPFEN? DU HOST DICH UNGEZOGEN?" er hot gemeynt ikh hob mikh ibergetun

00:05:05.480 --> 00:05:08.374
az ikh vil nisht geyn, biz ikh hob mikh

00:05:08.374 --> 00:05:11.518
hot men gezogt "⟨SCHAU, DAS IST MEINE ELTEREN⟩. WIR SINT LAGER MENSCHEN."

00:05:12.182 --> 00:05:15.180
un ⟨bay⟩ andern tog zenen arayn shoyn di rusn.

00:05:15.270 --> 00:05:16.732
un undz bafrayt.

00:05:16.418 --> 00:05:21.019
di host gehat in di lager a por, du host getseylt, a por nisim.

00:05:21.126 --> 00:05:22.082
nisim?

00:05:21.683 --> 00:05:22.571
yo.

00:05:22.594 --> 00:05:24.613
du kenst

00:05:25.429 --> 00:05:27.465
yetst zayn oyf

00:05:26.998 --> 00:05:29.202
dos greste nes iz geven dos

00:05:29.209 --> 00:05:32.730
vos der mayor hot undz geshikt NACH T- NACH

00:05:32.787 --> 00:05:37.725
Shargorod, ts- tsum dokter TEICH, tsum groysn tsienist, un dortn hobn mir ibergelebt

00:05:37.950 --> 00:05:39.867
vayl ven nisht dos

00:05:40.633 --> 00:05:43.968
UNK mir geven ale, di daytshn hobn likvidirt SOFORT.

00:05:44.447 --> 00:05:46.769
un dernokh dem ven ikh bin tsurikgekumen

00:05:46.945 --> 00:05:48.120
funem lager

00:05:48.295 --> 00:05:50.044
iz nokh geven milkhome.

00:05:50.826 --> 00:05:52.305
in Tshernovits hot men

00:05:51.298 --> 00:05:56.017
ober frier in di lager, du host gehat a por mol vos du host gezogt

00:05:54.775 --> 00:05:59.224
yo ikh hob, ge- geratevet di mentshn vos ikh hob zey bahaltn akht

00:05:59.618 --> 00:06:04.958
nokh dem hob ikh, geven a bokher vos er iz geven bay di daytshe, iz er antlofn, hob ikh im ibergetun

00:06:04.958 --> 00:06:09.088
un hob im opgevashn er zol zikh bahaltn, me zol im nisht khapn.

00:06:10.013 --> 00:06:13.601
un s'iz geven a por mol az d-

00:06:14.063 --> 00:06:15.941
di daytshn oder rume-

00:06:15.941 --> 00:06:18.393
zey hobn gedarfn shosn oyf

00:06:18.535 --> 00:06:21.063
ikh hob gehat az, ⟨EIN, EINE⟩ zakh

00:06:21.063 --> 00:06:22.325
vos nor

00:06:22.902 --> 00:06:26.392
in Mogilev hobn mir KENNEN GELERNT, ikh veys UNK geven a daytsh

00:06:26.398 --> 00:06:27.691
vos er hot zikh

00:06:28.170 --> 00:06:30.710
ikh v- JA, ikh hob im gemakht a plombe.

00:06:30.710 --> 00:06:33.480
kh'hob ge- ongehoybn tsu arbetn, hob ikh gemakht im a plombe

00:06:33.480 --> 00:06:36.433
hot er zikh mit undz a bisl azoy khavershaft gemakht

00:06:37.198 --> 00:06:39.170
un eyn mol zogt di froy "du veyst

00:06:39.170 --> 00:06:43.070
UNK undz veln mir im aynladn eyn mol tsu a mitog." bin ikh gegangen, hob ikh gekoyft a shtikl f-

00:06:43.070 --> 00:06:45.910
fleysh in geto, un zi hot gemakht a mitog

00:06:45.910 --> 00:06:48.950
un tsum trinken hob ikh gekoyft a fleshl mit epes tsum

00:06:48.950 --> 00:06:51.260
aza, ikh veys nisht vos s'iz geven vayn

00:06:51.260 --> 00:06:54.980
un dos iz geven gemakht fun metil spiritus, fun yidn gemakht

00:06:54.980 --> 00:06:56.728
un im iz shlekht gevorn.

00:06:56.728 --> 00:06:59.771
er hot ober nisht gezogt az er hot gegesn bay a yid

00:06:59.811 --> 00:07:05.087
vayl ven er zogt er hot undz, gegesn bay a yid un s'iz im shlekht gevorn, vet ⟨men undz⟩ geven SOFORT geshosn.

00:07:05.278 --> 00:07:06.048
er hot

00:07:06.156 --> 00:07:08.107
gehat ⟨epes azoy⟩ a

00:07:08.350 --> 00:07:11.259
er hot gez- gevust az undz kenen mir azoy nisht makhn

00:07:11.259 --> 00:07:14.059
un s'iz m- ibergegangen un, un dernokh dem

00:07:14.067 --> 00:07:16.184
hobn mir im farloyrn fun di oygn.

00:07:16.184 --> 00:07:17.800
vayl er iz geven nisht far-

00:07:17.800 --> 00:07:20.950
gekumen shpetsyel nokh m- er iz gekumen nor makhn aktsyes.

00:07:20.950 --> 00:07:22.771
shisn dort un shisn dort.

00:07:22.913 --> 00:07:25.686
mh dos iz geven mayn mazl vos er hot in mir gegleybt

00:07:25.686 --> 00:07:27.817
vos ikh hob im nisht gevolt farsamen.

00:07:30.304 --> 00:07:32.238
vos zol ikh nokh a sakh ⟨ertseyln⟩?

00:07:32.616 --> 00:07:35.096
zenen mir geven azoy vi me varft aroys

00:07:35.096 --> 00:07:40.196
undz varft men dem hunt nisht aroys oyf der gas vi undz ho- men dray yor, dray halb yor gehaltn dort.

00:07:40.196 --> 00:07:43.176
yeder hot gekent makhn vos er hot gevolt mit undz.

00:07:43.176 --> 00:07:46.852
hot gevolt a CHAYAL shisn a yid oyf der gas, hot er im gemegt shisn.

00:07:47.280 --> 00:07:50.767
s'iz geven hefker, hefker, hefker. ales hefker.

00:07:51.735 --> 00:07:53.838
vi azoy ikh hob dos ibergelebt

00:07:54.132 --> 00:07:58.615
un dernokh dem vayter shpeter oykh, shoyn in, shoyn in Tshernovits gekumen tsurik

00:07:58.671 --> 00:08:00.707
iz shoyn geven, nokh geven krig

00:08:00.730 --> 00:08:04.369
hob ikh vider ongehoybn mikh tsu dreyen ikh zol darfn geyn oyf der front

00:08:04.628 --> 00:08:05.528
un hob mikh

00:08:05.505 --> 00:08:10.527
ver iz geven dort in di lager, di DEUTSCHEN oder rus- n- di rumener?

00:08:05.528 --> 00:08:06.495
JA?

00:08:08.948 --> 00:08:15.020
neyn, rumener. d- in Mogilev iz geven, dos iz geven Rumenye, n- rumener, yo. dos iz rumener

00:08:11.614 --> 00:08:13.515
bloyz rumenen?

00:08:15.020 --> 00:08:15.982
vos zey hobn

00:08:15.982 --> 00:08:19.044
far vos fregt m- me shraybt haynt in der tsaytung

00:08:19.044 --> 00:08:22.610
f- ales, nor gevise zakhn UNK fargesn.

00:08:22.617 --> 00:08:25.547
in Ya- in Rumenye iz do a shtot Yasi

00:08:25.603 --> 00:08:27.470
hot men in eyn tog

00:08:27.477 --> 00:08:31.419
tsvelef toyznt yidn oysgeshosn, in eyn tog.

00:08:32.285 --> 00:08:36.214
far vos? un dos in a zuntik ven me darf geyn in kloyster davenen

00:08:36.214 --> 00:08:37.072
bay zey.

00:08:37.871 --> 00:08:40.101
un nokh a zakh hobn zey gemakht, di rumener

00:08:40.101 --> 00:08:42.521
afile di daytshe hobn dos nisht oysgetrakht.

00:08:42.577 --> 00:08:45.218
zey hobn genumen vagonen fun beheymes

00:08:45.218 --> 00:08:47.451
hot men arayngeshtupt hundert mentshn

00:08:47.541 --> 00:08:51.821
un m'hot f- di, di, vu se geyt arayn a bisl luft hot men farklept mit papir

00:08:51.945 --> 00:08:54.515
un m'hot di vagonen in AUGUST gefirt

00:08:54.515 --> 00:08:58.875
vokhn lang ahin un aher, ahin un aher.

00:08:58.875 --> 00:09:02.065
m'hot nor oyfgemakht di tir, aroysgenumen di toyte

00:09:02.065 --> 00:09:03.381
on vaser

00:09:03.522 --> 00:09:07.097
un on esn un on vu ts- on a BET SHIMUSH

00:09:07.097 --> 00:09:09.597
zenen zey ⟨geven⟩ hundert mentshn a vagon.

00:09:09.715 --> 00:09:13.070
dos hobn di rumener, dos iz a rumenishe ERFINDUNG geven

00:09:13.070 --> 00:09:17.438
tsu makhn di yidn ⟨zoln dan⟩, un az UNK oyfgemakht di tirn

00:09:17.438 --> 00:09:19.748
hobn zey sh- geshrign "vaser, vaser."

00:09:19.748 --> 00:09:23.228
hot men gezogt "gits vos ir hot, ales," hot men gegebn gold.

00:09:23.228 --> 00:09:25.220
m'hot aropgenumen fun zikh ales.

00:09:25.220 --> 00:09:30.178
zenen gekumen mit a emer vaser di rumener un hot oysgegosn dos vaser oyf der erd.

00:09:30.707 --> 00:09:32.456
dos iz geven dos tsveyte.

00:09:36.310 --> 00:09:40.686
se fargest zikh langzam. un in Bukarest hobn zey gemakht a zakh

00:09:40.686 --> 00:09:42.784
nor do veys ikh nisht dem emes.

00:09:42.773 --> 00:09:47.374
ober du darfst tseyln yetst vos iz pasirt mit di- mit, mit aykh.

00:09:42.857 --> 00:09:43.711
zey hob-

00:09:47.380 --> 00:09:48.574
ah, far mir?

00:09:48.574 --> 00:09:50.495
dos shoyn, fun andere nisht.

00:09:50.974 --> 00:09:53.904
nokh eyn zakh vos di rumener hobn gemakht.

00:09:51.852 --> 00:09:52.993
OKAY.

00:09:54.248 --> 00:09:57.484
zey hobn oyfgehongen dort vu men koylet beheymes

00:09:57.484 --> 00:09:59.405
hobn zey oyfgehongen yidn

00:09:59.479 --> 00:10:01.661
oyf di hokns, un hobn geshribn

00:10:01.661 --> 00:10:04.451
CARNE CUSER. kosher fleysh.

00:10:04.643 --> 00:10:06.766
yetst veys ikh ober eyn zakh nisht.

00:10:06.766 --> 00:10:08.586
tsi zey hobn zey oyfgehongen

00:10:08.693 --> 00:10:09.862
toyterheyt

00:10:09.862 --> 00:10:13.552
tsi lebndikerheyt. es ken zayn az zey hobn zey oyfgehongen lebndikerheyt

00:10:13.552 --> 00:10:15.642
un hobn geshribn CARNE CUSER.

00:10:15.642 --> 00:10:17.895
fun dem shraybt men nisht in di tsaytungen.

00:10:17.895 --> 00:10:20.696
men kusht zikh mitn ambasador mitn rumenishn.

00:10:20.696 --> 00:10:23.531
un me brengt rumenishe arbetorer aher, zoln do

00:10:23.531 --> 00:10:25.550
