vayl di sh- di baleboste, di goyte, iz geven krank oykh oyf boykh tifus

00:21:06.160 --> 00:21:08.443
un dos meydl irs hot dem

00:21:08.443 --> 00:21:11.772
dem nakh geshir geshit in gortn. di flign

00:21:11.830 --> 00:21:14.010
zenen gekumen, hobn ge-

00:21:14.010 --> 00:21:16.140
infestirt mistame undzer esn

00:21:16.140 --> 00:21:17.960
un azoy iz zi krank gevorn

00:21:17.960 --> 00:21:22.719
zi iz geven di eyntsike kranke, geven undz fir. ikh nisht un di VATER nisht un di MUTTER nisht.

00:21:22.719 --> 00:21:24.584
zi hot bakumen boykh tifus.

00:21:24.584 --> 00:21:27.146
un mit dem vos ikh hob zi gehaltn zeks vokhn

00:21:27.338 --> 00:21:28.648
mit ayz

00:21:28.958 --> 00:21:31.078
un di ho- zi iz oyfgeshtanen

00:21:31.078 --> 00:21:33.928
hot zi aropgenumen azoy a paruk, iz di gantse ⟨diz⟩ arop.

00:21:33.928 --> 00:21:36.478
di ale hor oyf eyn mol mit eyn ⟨diz⟩

00:21:36.518 --> 00:21:38.436
un azoy hot zi ibergelebt

00:21:40.011 --> 00:21:41.509
nisht in a shpitol

00:21:41.509 --> 00:21:43.409
un nisht mit doktoyrim, nor vos

00:21:43.409 --> 00:21:46.889
kh'hob nisht gelozt dos blut zol rinen, s'iz gevorn gefroyrn.

00:21:47.014 --> 00:21:49.103
s'a nes, a groys nes.

00:21:49.103 --> 00:21:52.424
ven men dertseylt es ken men dos nisht gleybn, ober s'iz

00:21:52.600 --> 00:21:53.674
dokh a fakt.

00:21:57.291 --> 00:21:59.293
vos nokh hot ir gevolt visn?

00:22:00.379 --> 00:22:02.313
s'iz shver geven, shver.

00:22:04.277 --> 00:22:10.973
shver, biz me zogt shoyn az s'iz UNK nisht zeks shoyn, s- me zogt shoyn yetst iz shoyn zibn milyon. es, der UNK shtimt nisht mer.

00:22:10.973 --> 00:22:12.421
s'iz nokh tsugekumen.

00:22:12.816 --> 00:22:14.177
ABER

00:22:14.655 --> 00:22:16.606
dos shpilt shoyn nisht keyn role yetst.

00:22:17.676 --> 00:22:19.172
tsi zeks, tsi zibn.

00:22:20.207 --> 00:22:24.841
vi azoy iz geven in vinter? s'iz geven zeyer kalt?

00:22:25.118 --> 00:22:28.251
vinter. mikh hot geratevet tsvey zakhn.

00:22:28.611 --> 00:22:33.904
di k- di koldres vos zi hot khasene gehat, un gebrakht tsvey koldres fun pukh

00:22:33.994 --> 00:22:35.223
hobn ir gemakht

00:22:35.223 --> 00:22:36.334
tsum geyn

00:22:36.728 --> 00:22:41.177
tsum glik hobn mir genumen a por zakhn oyf, in a rukzak.

00:22:41.183 --> 00:22:46.073
ven undz ze'mir gege- ales geven geleygt in a rentsl azoy vi di ale, ze'mir geven di

00:22:46.073 --> 00:22:48.568
dem ershte vokh ⟨voltn⟩ mir geven shoyn nisht geven

00:22:48.608 --> 00:22:50.762
vayl mentshn hobn ge- gegangen

00:22:51.021 --> 00:22:52.317
on gornisht.

00:22:52.317 --> 00:22:54.654
zi hot gemakht, dos iz geven ir idee.

00:22:54.654 --> 00:22:55.650
a rukzak.

00:22:55.650 --> 00:22:59.421
eyn koldre hob ikh gehat oyfn rukzak, azoy vi a turist

00:22:59.421 --> 00:23:01.106
un di tsveyte der ABA.

00:23:01.230 --> 00:23:03.434
un di koldres zenen geven fun pukh.

00:23:03.728 --> 00:23:06.205
di val- veykhe federn.

00:23:06.205 --> 00:23:08.644
un dos hit undz geratevet vinter.

00:23:08.644 --> 00:23:09.881
mit dem hobn mir zikh

00:23:10.090 --> 00:23:15.669
n- nisht gevorn derfroyrn. andersh ven, ven se, ven, hobn mir nisht di dekn vos zi hot mitgenumen

00:23:15.827 --> 00:23:18.622
voltn mir geven dem ershtn vinter shoyn gegangen.

00:23:19.202 --> 00:23:23.105
s'hot undz tsugeshpilt dos vos zi hot gehat a idee a por zakhn

00:23:23.105 --> 00:23:26.396
a hemd, a ⟨diz⟩, a por zakhn, vikhtike zakhn.

00:23:26.396 --> 00:23:30.603
un ikh hob mir langzam. ikh hob nisht gehat INSTRUMENTE dem ershtn vinter

00:23:30.660 --> 00:23:32.800
vayl ikh hob zey farloyrn, ibergelozt.

00:23:32.800 --> 00:23:34.454
hob ikh gearbet bay der brik.

00:23:34.454 --> 00:23:37.930
un dort hob ikh KENNEN GELERNT a ofitsir a daytshn, a viner

00:23:37.930 --> 00:23:39.986
un er hot gehert ikh red daytsh

00:23:40.009 --> 00:23:42.056
hot er ongehoybn tsu shitn nebekh

00:23:42.056 --> 00:23:44.284
zayn harts oystsushitn far mir.

00:23:44.284 --> 00:23:48.485
er hot gevust az ikh vel im nisht geyn ⟨farrotn⟩, hot oyf Hitlern geredt un oyf ales

00:23:48.485 --> 00:23:53.495
nu, m'hot im, ⟨ikh, hob ikh⟩ im gezogt az ikh bin ROFE SHINAIM, nor ikh hob nisht keyn INSTRUMENTE

00:23:53.495 --> 00:23:55.495
hot er mir gegebn di idee

00:23:55.495 --> 00:23:59.535
"gey, ⟨s'iz dort do⟩ ROFEIM SHINAIM rusishe vos zenen do, yidn

00:23:59.535 --> 00:24:02.762
bet az du host a patsyent, zol men dir ERLOBEN tsu arbetn."

00:24:02.762 --> 00:24:07.391
bin ikh gegangen, hob ikh getrofn UNK yidish- a yidishe froy, di froy vos kolboynik

00:24:07.414 --> 00:24:10.010
un zi hot mir ERLOBT ikh zol im n- onnemen dort

00:24:10.010 --> 00:24:11.402
un hob im gemakht tseyn

00:24:11.402 --> 00:24:15.958
hot er gezogt "du darfst shoyn nisht kumen tsu der arbet tsu der brik. ikh vel dir shikn patsyentn."

00:24:15.958 --> 00:24:19.119
hot er mir geshikt zayne CHAVERIM, un ikh hob zey gemakht tseyn

00:24:19.243 --> 00:24:20.148
un

00:24:21.083 --> 00:24:22.191
dernokh dem

00:24:22.281 --> 00:24:24.317
fun dem du host gehat gelt?

00:24:24.154 --> 00:24:28.538
vos? gelt, gelt. er ho- s'iz geven dort, ikh hob im gemakht a arbet

00:24:28.538 --> 00:24:34.299
ibergearbet fun zayne tseyn iz geblibn a shtikl gold, hob ikh es im gevolt gebn, zogt er "NEIN, DAS KANNST DU DIR NEHMEN."

00:24:34.299 --> 00:24:35.899
hot er es mir geshenkt.

00:24:35.950 --> 00:24:38.402
ikh zog dokh, undz hobn mir UNK dem gortn

00:24:38.402 --> 00:24:42.013
un dort iz gevaksn AGVANIYOT un nokh zakhn

00:24:42.013 --> 00:24:46.333
mayn MUTTER hot afile geganvet in gortn, geganvet. der foter hot gevust zi nemt

00:24:46.333 --> 00:24:51.203
un hot dos getrogn in geto in hot dos farteylt bay ire bakante vos zi hot gehat nebekh dort.

00:24:51.407 --> 00:24:52.565
undz ho'mir

00:24:52.622 --> 00:24:56.508
relativ, relativ vos hobn mir gevoynt AUSSER dem geto

00:24:56.508 --> 00:25:02.370
hobn mir gehat a bisl laykhter vi di. ABER yidn zenen mir geven trots dem. dem shtern hobn mir trots dem getrogn.

00:25:02.595 --> 00:25:09.136
un az a CHAYAL hot gevolt shisn a g- a mentsh oyf der gas, hot er im gemegt UNK shisn, hot im keyner nisht gefregt far vos host im geshosn.

00:25:09.750 --> 00:25:11.156
s'iz geven a lager.

00:25:11.156 --> 00:25:13.594
a VERNICHTUNGS lager tsum, tsum, tsum

00:25:13.594 --> 00:25:17.068
nisht tsum lebn. tsum, me zol shtarbn hot men undz ahingefirt.

00:25:21.377 --> 00:25:24.577
yo, un dos iz ales geblibn biz tsum hayntikn tog.

00:25:25.900 --> 00:25:29.353
ikh gey aroys fun der shtub, vel ikh nisht geyn on a zeyger

00:25:29.427 --> 00:25:31.457
vayl ⟨ikh bin gekumen sh-⟩ m-

00:25:31.457 --> 00:25:36.737
ven ikh hob nisht dem z- dem zeyger un di rumener tapt nisht on un nemt dem zeyger hob ikh, hot er mir geven geshosn.

00:25:37.003 --> 00:25:39.882
vos iz geven mit di zeyger? tseyl.

00:25:37.088 --> 00:25:37.959
vayl er hot

00:25:39.045 --> 00:25:41.874
ikh bin aroysgegangen fri. ikh hob nisht gevust az zey hobn

00:25:41.880 --> 00:25:43.767
f- rekhts tsu shisn dray tog.

00:25:43.767 --> 00:25:47.274
kh'hob gehert se kumt di rumenishe armey tsurik IM JAHRE fertsik

00:25:47.280 --> 00:25:51.543
bin ikh gegangen zey onkukn, un ikh shtey azoy. ruft mikh a CH- a zelner

00:25:51.600 --> 00:25:52.606
"shtey dort."

00:25:52.849 --> 00:25:55.357
zogt er "bist a JIDAN?" zog ikh yo.

00:25:55.633 --> 00:25:59.600
nemt er mikh un firt mikh arayn in a gortn, un dort iz shoyn eyner gelegn vos hot zikh

00:25:59.600 --> 00:26:02.710
gevorfn. er iz shoyn geven geshosn ober er hot nokh gelebt.

00:26:03.278 --> 00:26:06.782
un firt mikh er zol mikh shisn nebn dem, lebn dem andern.

00:26:06.788 --> 00:26:08.126
azoy vi ikh bl-

00:26:08.126 --> 00:26:12.620
bin shoyn geven tsvey meter fun yenem, un UNK blaybt er shteyn un git a tap bay der hant.

00:26:12.627 --> 00:26:15.459
hob ikh gehat dem zeyger vos zi hot mir gekoyft tsu der khasene

00:26:15.459 --> 00:26:18.527
gib ikh dem zeyger. gib ikh im dem zeyger un vart vayter.

00:26:18.769 --> 00:26:20.467
zogt er "gey aheym."

00:26:23.258 --> 00:26:24.703
un dem andern tog

00:26:25.080 --> 00:26:27.750
iz geven bay undz in der gas a familye fun rusn

00:26:27.750 --> 00:26:33.750
vos der zun iz avek mit di rusn. er hot gemeynt di rusn veln blaybn in Tshernovits, hot er gelozt di gantse familye, zeks mentshn

00:26:34.362 --> 00:26:37.781
nu, SOFORT hobn di ukrayner dort vos hobn gevoynt in undzer gas

00:26:38.445 --> 00:26:40.501
gemakht a den- ANGEZEIGT

00:26:40.501 --> 00:26:48.041
gekumen zey nemen tsum shisn. dos iz geven in di ershte dray tog ven m'hot gemegt shisn. nayn hundert mentshn hot men demlst oysgeshosn in Tshernovits in di dray tog.

00:26:48.672 --> 00:26:53.897
mayn MUTTER hot UNK zey gevolt helfn a bisl trogn a gloz tey oder a flash tey

00:26:53.953 --> 00:26:58.008
iz zi arayngegangen demlst vu di zelner zenen geven dort, hot men zi oykh shoyn gefirt

00:26:58.008 --> 00:26:58.886
aroys.

00:26:58.886 --> 00:27:01.287
ikh ze me firt aroys di MUTTER fun dem hoyf

00:27:01.378 --> 00:27:07.053
mit nokh zeks mentshn mit CHAYALIM, hob ikh shoyn gevust, vayl ikh hob mikh shoyn durkhgegangen dem ershtn tog funem shisn

00:27:07.053 --> 00:27:10.029
bin ikh tsugelofn zogn az dos iz mayn MUTTER

00:27:10.238 --> 00:27:12.032
nem- zogt er "kum du oykh"

00:27:12.032 --> 00:27:14.327
un firt undz aroys oyf der hoypt gas.

00:27:14.327 --> 00:27:17.809
ikh hob a plan fun Tshernovits genoy der plats vu me hot undz gefirt.

00:27:18.152 --> 00:27:21.133
un hot undz oysgeshtelt ale akht in der SHURA

00:27:21.207 --> 00:27:22.466
in der rey

00:27:22.776 --> 00:27:26.651
un ⟨az me⟩ nemt shoyn, makht UNK aroystsunemen di, di ko- koyln

00:27:26.775 --> 00:27:33.839
iz kumt un oyf dem zelbn trotuar vu undz ze'mir geshtanen efsher fuftsik meter vayter kumt a CHA- a ofitsir a rumenisher.

00:27:33.930 --> 00:27:37.603
dos iz d- geven a, mistame a malekh, ober ongetun in a

00:27:37.677 --> 00:27:38.818
uniform.

00:27:41.119 --> 00:27:45.815
m'iz oyfgehert shoyn tsu shisn vayl mir, az se geyt a ofitsir ken zikh trefn im oykh.

00:27:45.815 --> 00:27:46.828
hobn zey oyfgehert

00:27:46.828 --> 00:27:50.141
un azoy vi der ofitsir iz durkhgegangen bin ikh aroysgeshprungen

00:27:50.839 --> 00:27:53.988
un hobn mir a por UNK, vos heyst ikh hob mir gemakht a

00:27:54.130 --> 00:27:56.031
ikh veys nisht far vos me shist

00:27:56.374 --> 00:27:59.692
hot er mir gegebn azoy vi er vil, er vil baytn ⟨diz⟩.

00:27:59.783 --> 00:28:02.055
hot er mir gegebn a flig mit der hant

00:28:02.213 --> 00:28:04.924
un hot zikh kalye gemakht dem zeyger.

00:28:07.123 --> 00:28:10.036
un ikh hob dernokhdem im farrokhtn dem zeyger

00:28:10.110 --> 00:28:14.306
un hob im gegebn nokh a matone, dem zeyde fun mayn pape, a goldenem zeyger.

00:28:14.329 --> 00:28:15.515
hot er mikh

00:28:15.515 --> 00:28:17.461
di MUTTER un di zeks mentshn

00:28:17.670 --> 00:28:19.338
aroysgelozt lebndik.
